Text: Verify CSM RCS Thruster B3 - OFF & Radar Xponder - Off
cb AC BUS A: RNDZ RDR - close (Wait 30 sec)
cb AC BUS A: RNG/RNG RT ALT/ALT RT - close
cb FLIGHT DISPLAYS: RNG/RNG RT ALT/ALT RT - close
SLEW Left 18 sec, then Right, Down, Left, Up , monitor FDAI Needles
SLEW Right, Down, Left, Up, monitor FDAI Needles & X-pointer
X-pointers and FDAI Needles Vary Between ±5 deg
After 12 sec, Rng Tape Drives to 195, NO TRACK Lt - Off
NO TRACK Lt - On, Wait 10 sec
NO TRACK Lt - On (Off After 12 sec)
F 16 78 RANGE, RANGE RATE, TFI (.01nm, fps, min-sec)
cb AC BUS A: RNDZ RDR - open
